Title: Out of Touch
Writer: Andy Deliana, Enkel Demi, Randy Vandegrift
Actors: Gentjan Zenelaj, Rozi Kotani, Laertis Vasiliou, Tatiana Cotiuba
Plot: Two men, a former ministry chief and his business partner, have less than 48 hours to save their jobs and reputations. An absurd chain of events threatens to destroy everyone in this fast paced crime thriller.
